                     <rs type="fn" role="recipient"><rs type="person" ref="#pe__jakob_maeserl_QGW_II_I_121">Jakob den Maeserlein</rs></rs>. <rs type="fn" role="other"><triggerstring n="fn">Zu Schirm</triggerstring> setzen sich
